📌 Warframe Relic Reward Value Calculator

Live Site: https://mosestyle.github.io/Warframe-Relic/


---

🔎 What This Project Does

This project is a static web-based tool that allows Warframe players to:

Select up to 4 Void Relics

View all possible Prime rewards

See Platinum values (90-day median from Warframe.market)

Sort rewards by Platinum value

Instantly see which relics are:

🟢 Available / Unvaulted

🔴 Vaulted



All relic data, price data, and vault status are automatically updated using GitHub Actions workflows.

No backend server.
No manual data editing.
Fully automated.


---

💡 The Core Problem It Solves

Warframe relic decisions are often inefficient and fragmented.

Players frequently:

Don’t know which relics are currently vaulted

Don’t know which rewards are actually valuable

Check multiple websites before making a decision

Waste time opening low-value relics

Make relic decisions without price awareness


Each relic contains multiple rewards with different drop chances, and the game does not provide economic insight into their real value.

This project solves that by combining:

✔ Relic drop tables
✔ Drop chance percentages
✔ Platinum market values
✔ Vault status visibility
✔ Natural relic sorting
✔ A fast searchable relic picker UI

It transforms relic selection from guesswork into a data-driven decision.


